stepNumber":4,"title":"Night Routine","duration":"30 minutes","instructions":["Before going to sleep tonight:","Avoid phone usage 30 minutes before bed.","Instead:","stretch lightly practice slow breathing allow the body to relax Quality sleep supports recovery and hormonal balance."],"whyThisWorks":"Better sleep supports hormone balance, recovery, and calmer nervous-system function."},{"type":"close","message":"Day 2 is complete.","secondaryMessage":"Strengthen control over urges, continue calming the nervous system, and reinforce the muscles that\nsupport sexual health."}]'::jsonb
