ation - Bodyweight Squats","instructions":["Stand with feet shoulder-width apart","Lower hips like sitting on a chair","Keep chest upright","Push through heels to stand up","15 reps × 3 sets"],"rest":"20 seconds"},{"name":"Circulation Boost - Brisk Walk / Light Jog","instructions":["Take a 20 minute brisk walk or light jog.","Improve blood circulation","Reduce stress hormones","Support cardiovascular health"],"duration":"20 minute brisk walk"}]},{"type":"action_step","stepNumber":5,"title":"Night Routine","duration":"30 minutes","instructions":["Before sleep tonight:","Avoid phone usage 30 minutes before bed.","Instead:","stretch lightly practice slow breathing relax your body Better sleep supports recovery and hormone balance."],"whyThisWorks":"Better sleep supports hormone balance, recovery, and calmer nervous-system function."},{"type":"close","message":"Day 5 is complete.","secondaryMessage":"Strengthen mental confidence, reduce performance pressure, and continue reinforcing healthy\nhabits and physical strength."}]'::jsonb
