 seconds"},{"name":"Hormone Activation - Bodyweight Squats (Improved)","instructions":["Stand with feet shoulder-width apart","Lower hips slowly","Keep chest upright","Push through heels to stand up","18 reps × 3 sets"],"rest":"20 seconds"},{"name":"Circulation Boost - Brisk Walk / Light Jog","instructions":["Take a 22 minute brisk walk or light jog.","Improve cardiovascular strength","Increase blood circulation","Reduce stress hormones"],"duration":"22 minute brisk walk"}]},{"type":"action_step","stepNumber":5,"title":"Night Routine","duration":"30 minutes","instructions":["Before sleep tonight:","Avoid phone usage 30 minutes before bed.","Instead:","stretch lightly take slow breaths allow your body to relax Quality sleep supports recovery and hormonal balance."],"whyThisWorks":"Better sleep supports hormone balance, recovery, and calmer nervous-system function."},{"type":"close","message":"Day 8 is complete.","secondaryMessage":"Build momentum in your recovery, begin reaching your daily hydration level, and strengthen pelvic\nmuscles with a slightly improved exercise routine."}]'::jsonb
